metadata.name: Junk #2
metadata.description:
To become true NFTs, Crypto-Junkies had to transfer their immortal genesis souls to a different dimension. Cleaner. Better. 2D Genesis ERC721 1/1 PFP.
This is no pixelated lazy render collection. Every Junk was rebuilt pixel by pixel in a 32 by 32 grid. Handmade with love.
 All genesis utility of the 3D voxel collection was moved to this token. Hodl tight to not lose your genesis benefits. Tokens got airdropped to their holders. No mint. Only for holders.
